      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "LAN (Local Area Network)",
        "zh": "局域网（LAN）",
        "en": "LAN (Local Area Network)"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "その名前のとおり、社内や学校内といった、狭い範囲のコンピュータで構成される小規模なネットワークのこと。",
        "zh": "顾名思义，指由公司内、校园内等狭小范围内的计算机所构成的小规模网络。",
        "en": "As its name suggests, a small-scale network composed of computers within a narrow range such as inside a company or a school."
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
